---
import '@fontsource/ibm-plex-mono';
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/lexcorp-logo.svg?v=1" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>404 - Página No Encontrada | Andrés Almeida</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Error 404 - La página que buscas no existe. Regresa al terminal principal del portfolio de Andrés Almeida." />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
		
		<!-- Open Graph -->
		<meta property="og:title" content="404 - Página No Encontrada" />
		<meta property="og:description" content="Error 404 - La página solicitada no fue encontrada." />
		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-terminal-bg text-terminal-text font-mono min-h-screen">
		<div class="min-h-screen p-4 flex flex-col max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Terminal Header -->
			<div class="bg-terminal-bg border-b border-terminal-accent/30 p-4 flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
					<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
					<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
					<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
					<span class="ml-4 text-terminal-accent font-semibold">ERROR TERMINAL</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
					<span class="text-terminal-accent/80">Sistema v2.4.1</span>
					<div class="bg-terminal-accent/20 px-3 py-1 rounded border border-terminal-accent/40">
						<span id="error-time">--:--:--</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- 404 Content -->
			<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-6">
				<!-- ASCII Art -->
				<div class="text-terminal-accent text-xs font-mono leading-tight">
					<pre>
 ██╗  ██╗ ██████╗ ██╗  ██╗
 ██║  ██║██╔═████╗██║  ██║
 ███████║██║██╔██║███████║
 ╚════██║████╔╝██║╚════██║
      ██║╚██████╔╝     ██║
      ╚═╝ ╚═════╝      ╚═╝
					</pre>
				</div>

				<!-- Error Message -->
				<div class="border border-terminal-accent/30 bg-terminal-accent/5 p-6 rounded max-w-2xl">
					<div class="text-terminal-accent text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
						>> ERROR: PÁGINA NO ENCONTRADA
					</div>
					<div class="text-terminal-text/90 space-y-3">
						<p>La página solicitada no existe en este sistema.</p>
						<p>Verifica la URL o regresa al terminal principal.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Terminal Output -->
				<div class="bg-terminal-bg border border-terminal-accent/30 rounded p-4 max-w-2xl text-left">
					<div class="text-terminal-accent mb-2">
						root@portafolio:~$ ls -la /pages/
					</div>
					<div class="text-terminal-text/80 text-sm space-y-1">
						<div>total 2</div>
						<div>drwxr-xr-x  2 andres andres 4096 Dec 15 12:34 .</div>
						<div>drwxr-xr-x  3 andres andres 4096 Dec 15 12:34 ..</div>
						<div>-rw-r--r--  1 andres andres 1024 Dec 15 12:34 index.astro</div>
						<div>-rw-r--r--  1 andres andres  512 Dec 15 12:34 portafolio.astro</div>
					</div>
					<div class="text-terminal-accent mt-3">
						root@portafolio:~$ <span class="animate-blink">█</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Navigation Buttons -->
				<div class="flex space-x-4">
					<a href="/" 
					   class="bg-terminal-accent/20 border border-terminal-accent/40 px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-terminal-accent/30 transition-colors text-terminal-accent font-semibold">
						← Volver al Terminal Principal
					</a>
					<a href="/portafolio" 
					   class="bg-terminal-accent/10 border border-terminal-accent/30 px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-terminal-accent/20 transition-colors text-terminal-text">
						Ver Portafolio →
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Help Text -->
				<div class="text-terminal-accent/60 text-sm">
					<p>Tip: Usa los comandos <code class="bg-terminal-accent/20 px-2 py-1 rounded">help</code> en cualquier terminal para ver las opciones disponibles.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<script>
			// Update time
			function updateErrorTime() {
				const now = new Date();
				const timeString = now.toLocaleTimeString([], { hour12: false });
				const timeElement = document.getElementById('error-time');
				if (timeElement) {
					timeElement.textContent = timeString;
				}
			}

			updateErrorTime();
			setInterval(updateErrorTime, 1000);
		</script>
	</body>
</html> 